{"type": "article", "id": 9228, "title": "06/67 Monterey Sneaker 春季系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-06T06:53:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234929AbiRNjshHePmg3nJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t春夏交接，帆布鞋正当道，SeaVees 推出了 06/67 Monterey Sneaker 春季系列，鞋子的设计灵感来源于 1967 年 6 月的 Monterey 音乐节。该系列全部采用鲜粉嫩的颜色，如浅粉色，粉黄色，粉蓝色等等，表达活泼和清新感，视觉上如同甜美的果汁一般。材料上，鞋面选用了天然抗菌和防敏感的竹帆布。目前这款鞋子在<a href=\"http://seavees.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> SeaVees 官方网站</a>已经可以接受预定。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234928dkBIHgJ8WyQsXCbv.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052349288fvGTNWhn7sSCmKL.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234929gOxqfEwVothZW8BU.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}